TychusSCVAutoTurret.Description:
Automated defensive structure. Auto-Turrets can be salvaged.

Can attack ground and air units.
Detector
TychusSCVAutoTurret.Name: Auto-Turret

TychusWarhoundAutoTurret.Description:
Deploy an automated defensive turret. Turrets gain the same gear bonuses as Sirius himself. Times out after 60 seconds. Holds up to 5 charges.

Can attack ground and air units.
TychusWarhoundAutoTurret.Name: Warhound Turret

TychusOdin.Description:
The Odin is a massive siege walker capable of leveling entire cities.

Can attack ground and air units.
TychusOdin.Name: Odin

TychusResearchCenter.Description:
A hideout for premier Outlaws.

Enables:
- Recruit Outlaw
- Revive Outlaw
TychusResearchCenter.Name: Joeyray's Bar

TychusReaper.Description: One of the Guns. Adept at dealing heavy damage against individual targets. Can use Demolition Charge.**Can attack ground and air units**
TychusReaper.Name: Crooked Sam

TychusWarhound.Description: One of the Guns. Adept at deploying Turrets and imbuing both himself and his Turrets with special abilities. Can use Deploy Warhound Turret.**Can attack ground and air units**
TychusWarhound.Name: James "Sirius" Sykes

TychusHERC.Description: One of the Muscle. Adept at taking damage and dealing it back. Can use Heavy Impact.**Can attack ground units**
TychusHERC.Name: Rob "Cannonball" Boswell

TychusGhost.Description: One of the Fixers. Adept at taking control of enemy units. Can use Dominate. Can be upgraded to be a Detector.**Can attack ground and air units**
TychusGhost.Name: Vega

TychusMedic.Description: One of the Fixers. Adept at healing friendly units and preventing damage. Can use Reinvigorating Burst. Can be upgraded to be a Detector.
TychusMedic.Name: Lt. Layna Nikara

TychusMarauder.Description: One of the Muscle. Adept at supporting friendly units and dealing with armored ground units. Can use Deploy Revitalizer.**Can attack ground units**
TychusMarauder.Name: Kev "Rattlesnake" West

TychusMarauderHealingWard.Description: Places a structure on the ground that heals all friendly units in an area around the structure for 2% of their life every second.
TychusMarauderHealingWard.Name: Revitalizer

TychusSpectre.Description: One of the Fixers. Adept at dealing with masses of enemy units and waves. Can use Ultrasonic Pulse. Can be upgraded to be a Detector. **Can attack ground and air units**
TychusSpectre.Name: Nux

TychusFirebat.Description: One of the Muscle. Adept at dealing with masses of weak ground units. Can use Oil Spill.**Can attack ground units**
TychusFirebat.Name: Miles "Blaze" Lewis

TychusCoop.Description: One of the Guns. Adept at all aspects of combat. Can use Shredder Grenade.**Can attack ground and air units**
TychusCoop.Name: Tychus Findlay

TychusArmory.Description:
Contains gear upgrades for the Muscle: Blaze, Cannonball, and Rattlesnake.

Enables:
- Blaze from Joeyray's Bar
- Cannonball from Joeyray's Bar
- Rattlesnake from Joeyray's Bar
TychusArmory.Name: Muscle Armory

TychusCommandCenter.Description:
Primary structure. Used to receive gathered resources. Can use the Lift Off ability.

Enables:
- SCVs
TychusCommandCenter.Name: Command Center

TychusCommandCenterFlying.Description: Primary structure. Must land to receive resources, produce units, or use abilities.
TychusCommandCenterFlying.Name: Command Center

TychusSCV.Description:
Basic worker unit. Can gather resources, build Terran structures, and repair.

Can attack ground units.
TychusSCV.Name: SCV

Refinery.Description: Built over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
Refinery.Name: Refinery

TychusMercCompound.Description:
Contains gear upgrades for the Guns: Tychus, Crooked Sam, and Sirius.

Enables:
- Crooked Sam from Joeyray's Bar
- Sirius from Joeyray's Bar
TychusMercCompound.Name: Gunslingers' Hideout

TychusEngineeringBay.Description:
Contains upgrades for Tychus, his Outlaws, and the Odin.

Enables:
- Auto-Turrets from SCVs
TychusEngineeringBay.Name: Engineering Bay

TychusGhostAcademy.Description:
Contains gear upgrades for the Fixers: Vega, Nux, and Lt. Nikara.

Enables:
- Vega from Joeyray's Bar
- Nux from Joeyray's Bar
- Lt. Nikara from Joeyray's Bar
TychusGhostAcademy.Name: Fixers' Safehouse

TychusMedivacPlatform.Description: Transport platform. Can instantly transport Tychus' combat units in the target area to a targeted location, healing and cloaking them on drop-off.
TychusMedivacPlatform.Name: Medivac Platform
